<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="condemn-vt">condemn <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kən'dem/    美 /kən'dem/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>谴责；指责：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She knew that society would <strong>condemn</strong> her <strong>for</strong> leaving her children. 
她知道社会会谴责她遗弃自己的孩子。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-sentence">2.<strong>[常用于被动语态]宣判 (某人) 有罪；判 (某人) 刑(sentence)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was found guilty and <strong>condemned to death</strong>. 
他被裁定有罪，判了死刑。</p></div></div>